# Data artifacts (scraped / enriched datasets, raw caches).
# Anchored to the repo root so it does NOT match the src/.../data/ package.
# Glob the contents (not the dir) so the curated golden set can be re-included.
/data/*
*.jsonl

# The golden eval set is curated test data, not a generated artifact — keep it
# version-controlled. Re-included after the /data/ and *.jsonl ignores above.
!/data/golden_set.jsonl

